ont-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>收入下降<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>现金流紧张<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>等问题<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>都是<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>急需调整的，生菜地图在商场的实战演练中促成<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>长<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>期的发展战略，其中包括有效通过对目标人流做流量细化分析，相似位置等，精准扩大目标用户并形成促销，从而增加商场收入，与此同时还包括人流密集度导航、人流数据分析等功能有效降低消费者对进入到密闭场所的担忧，从而增加客流。生菜地图<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>还<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>致力于对目标群体提供<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>不同<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>优惠券以及提供目标导航服务的功能，优化<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>用户<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>购物体验，为购物中心以及商户<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>进行<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>长期发展注能。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>而针对消费行为和习惯在疫情之后所带来的长期改变，如趋于理性消费，并对安全性、趋同性、便捷性等需求更高的趋势下，生菜地图为商场提供包括人流密集度导航、位置共享、精准消费者画像，优化商场私域流量，并更大范围<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>触达营销目标。另外，生菜地图所提供<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>目标导航，契合包括对洗手间、充电桩、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>移动电源、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>停车场等已知刚性需求<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的精准导航<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，同时针对消费者<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>更加理性<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>趋向目标购物的行为，生菜地图也提供了对购买区域以及熟知品牌商家的精准导航，节约<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>消费者的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>找寻时间，<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>快速促成消费者的成单<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>。另外通过位置共享等功能，加强消费者之间的互动<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>&nbsp;<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，增加趋同性的社交类型消费。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>未来展望<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-fareast-font-family:\'等线 Light\';\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);font-size:13.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>2020年初爆发的疫情，使得中国乃至全球的零售行业面临着巨大挑战。市场中的变幻莫测带来的经营困境以及突如其来的疫情给消费行为习惯带来的长期变化，为零售企业尤其是多业态购物中心的经营带来了前所未有的挑战。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>为了更好地与多业态购物中心等企业同舟共济、共谋发展机遇，生菜地图从拓宽运营渠道的角度思考，提出以多业态购物中心当前困境与消费者多重变化为重心，坚持为用户提供完美导航体验的同时，为企业提供拓宽私域流量的用户经营方案。我们希望能够籍此机会与企业共谋长远发展，为合作伙伴提供解决方案，以消费者触达、购物体验及用户洞察为基础，落地实施该蓝图。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <p class=\'p\' style=\'margin-top:7.5000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;\nmargin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\'><span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;color:rgb(238,236,224);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\nmso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\'>来源：生菜科技<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\'>\n   <p class=\'p\' style=\'margin-top:7.5000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;\nmargin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\'><span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(238,236,224);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\nmso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\'>文章编写：首席战略官Roxanane&nbsp;&nbsp;Guo<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\'>\n   <p class=\'p\' style=\'margin-top:7.5000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:7.5000pt;\nmargin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\'><span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(238,236,224);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);\nmso-shading:rgb(255,255,255);\'>整理编辑：产品运营Alan&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);\nletter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\'>\n   \n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'Times New Roman\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'宋体\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'Calibri Light\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'等线 Light\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'Calibri\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'等线\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'等线\';\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:\'微软雅黑\';\n}\n\np.MsoNormal{\nmso-style-name:正文;\nmso-style-parent:\'\';\nmargin-bottom:8.0000pt;\nli