1.0000pt;\'>&nbsp;<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   LS Technology -Letts Map<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>&nbsp;<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;Chief Strategy Officer<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(91,155,213);\nfont-style:italic;\'>R<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(91,155,213);\nfont-style:italic;\'>oxanne Guo<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>新冠疫情这一“黑天鹅”自2020年初爆发以来，对全球经济尤其是消费零售企业带来了剧烈影响，此影响仍在持续蔓延并波及全球。 <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>而受疫情影响，民众居家隔离，尽量减少不必要外出，外加上对于购物中心，商场等密闭空间传染风险高的担忧，多业态购物中心客源短期内受到较大负面影响；而疫情之后的消费环境，零售企业尤其是多业态购物中心也将面临更理性谨慎和挑剔的消费者。如何应对现金流客源等困境和消费行为习惯长期改变，也成为多业态购物中心涅槃重生的核心。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>多业态购物中心面临多重挑战<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-fareast-font-family:\'等线 Light\';\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);font-size:13.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>德勤与中国连锁企业报告显示，今年3月中国全国零售行业报告显示，多于60%的多业态购物中心客源降低超过50%，而其中餐饮、商店店铺均受到巨大影响。此外，80%多业态购物中心2020第一季度收入下降，其中60%此类购物中心下降至30%以上。与此同时受疫情影响，一半以上的零售企业，包括多业态购物中心，预计未来3个月至12月份将出现资金短缺情况。面对现金流问题，主要采取改善运营资金，新增融资策略；于此同时，本次疫情也让更多零售企业意识到线上业务发展的重要性，83%的零售企业表示将发展线上销售渠道、加快线上线下整合；并有超过一半的零售企业也有意愿加强数字化生态建设，多元化发展，增加体验性，构建完整一体化的营销体系。（数据来源：中国连锁经营协会）<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>疫情改变消费心智，多业态购物中心<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>需<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>加强购物体验<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>2020年上半年社会消费品零售总额下降7.6%， 全国网上零售额51501亿元，同比增长7.3%（数据来源：国家统计局）。在网上消费成为在不同年龄段的消费群体中成为常态的同时，新冠疫情也促成新的消费趋势，消费更加理性。贝恩咨询研究发现，对于刚需消费品、可选消费品以及耐用消费品都有超过30%的消费者趋于经济实惠选项；同时超过20%的消费者将对母婴、个护以及食品等必选消费品增加消费支出。而日渐兴起的线上销售模式也将延续到疫情之后。（数据来源：贝恩咨询）<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>疫情对消费心理和行为带<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>来了<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>较大影响。消费者将<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>会<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>更<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>加<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>强调消费的安全性<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，无论是<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>消费环境<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>、<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>产品<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>或者<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>服务的安全性<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>都<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>将会得到极大提高。尤其是对于购物环境的要求，封闭空间的病毒消杀、客流筛查以及对电梯间、卫生间、母婴室、停车场等高频接触空间都存在隐患。其次，消费者“趋同性”购心理<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>强化，个体消费受群体消费影响效应<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>变更加<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>凸显，<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>在<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>未来以社交为基础的购买行为将快速提升。第三，消费者对便捷性和速度的要求<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>也<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>将进一步强化，同时配送时效也将成为消费者购买行为中更为重要的决策要素。最后，消费者基于品牌预设的“目标购物”“速战速决”等购物行为将成为<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>主流<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，同时消费者在购买行为上消耗的时间将进一步缩减。（信息来源：罗兰贝格）<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>多业态购物中心的私域流量与数字化转型相结合，赋能消费者购物体验<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>在过去几十年，中国经济高速增长，面对巨大的流量红利，如何抢占市场、扩大规模成为了企业惯有的思维模式。而该思维模式背后的假设是环境的相对稳定和过往增长逻辑的延续，但随着存量市场时代的来临以及突发性事件冲击，该思维模式所依赖的假设逻辑变量<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>变的不在稳定<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>，此次疫情就是一个例证。未来的企业需要思考如何能够在多元动态的商业环境中，做到核心竞争力持久的能力，仅靠规模的时代不仅已经消失，而且存在“轰然倒塌”的巨大风险。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>然而虽然从2003至2004年细分行业同比增速可看出，2003年“非典”之后，餐饮、酒店、旅游等出现触底反弹的现象，然而17年后的今天，电子商务和物流供应链的发展带来消费习惯与消费场景的巨大变化，疫情期间的消费诉求得以补偿，同时疫情覆盖面广，对于消费者信心影响也会大于“非典” 时期，因此在疫情后期，爆发性增长可能性较小。短期而言，除了加强融资与现金流管理，线上经营也是拓宽消费渠道，拉动销售增长的“战时”经营策略。而从中长期发展来看，多业态购物中心不同于虚拟购物平台，其独特的场景体验难以被线上购物代替，因此专注消费心理受疫情影响后带来的长期变化，通过数字化转型赋能商场购物体验，做好购物中心的私域流量管理同样意义重大。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>生菜地图<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>助力多业态购物中心管理发展。<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'等线 Light\';mso-ascii-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';\nmso-hansi-font-family:\'Calibri Light\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(46,117,181);\nfont-size:13.0000pt;\'>\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>\n   \n    &nbsp;\n   <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:0.2500pt;\nfont-weight:bold;font-style:italic;\'>生菜地图的多项<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:0.2500pt;\nfont-weight:bold;font-style:italic;\'>功能<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;letter-spacing:0.2500pt;\nfont-weight:bold;font-style:italic;\'>优势助力购物中心的发展<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';letter-spacing:0.2500pt;\nfont-weight:bold;font-style:italic;\'>\n     <span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>生菜地图<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>是<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>龙狮科技<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>与<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>新加坡国立大学设立<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>的<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:11.0000pt;\'>专项研发实验室，<span style=\'mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:等线;mso-as